<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Indians in Ghana</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9933 0%, #138808 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .welcome-message {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .welcome-message h2 {
            color: #FF9933;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .welcome-message p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .membership-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #f8f9fa 100%);
            border: 2px solid #FF9933;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .membership-card h3 {
            color: #138808;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .membership-details {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 20px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FF9933;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .benefits {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .benefits h3 {
            color: #138808;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .benefits-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .benefits-list li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 30px;
        }
        
        .benefits-list li:before {
            content: "âœ“";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #138808;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .benefits-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9933 0%, #138808 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #FF9933;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .membership-details {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .detail-item {
                min-width: auto;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .welcome-message h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Indians in Ghana</h1>
            <p>Connecting the Indian Community</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-message">
                <h2>Welcome, {{firstName}}! ðŸŽ‰</h2>
                <p>We're thrilled to have you join our vibrant Indian community in Ghana!</p>
                <p style="color: #FF9933; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px;">
                    Your profile will be reviewed by the admin and then your membership card/certificate will be provided with other features.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="membership-card">
                <h3>Your Membership Details</h3>
                <div class="membership-details">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Member Name</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{fullName}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Membership Number</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">#{{membershipNumber}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Valid Until</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{validationDate}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefits">
                <h3>What You Can Enjoy:</h3>
                <ul class="benefits-list">
                    <li>Access to exclusive deals and discounts from Indian businesses</li>
                    <li>Digital membership card with QR code for easy verification</li>
                    <li>Connect with other Indian community members</li>
                    <li>Stay updated on community events and festivals</li>
                    <li>Support local Indian businesses and entrepreneurs</li>
                    <li>Access to cultural programs and networking events</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="cta-button">Access Your Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
                <ol style="color: #666; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Log into your account using your registered email</li>
                    <li>Complete your profile if you haven't already</li>
                    <li>Browse available deals and start saving</li>
                    <li>Connect with the community</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Indians in Ghana</strong> - Connecting Community, Creating Value</p>
            <p>This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
            <p>Email: {{supportEmail}} | Website: www.indiansinghana.com</p>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>This email was sent to {{email}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
